The paper discusses shared control in teleoperation, which is a topic related to robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the allocation of control power between human and robot, which is a topic related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper introduces a multi-source uncertainty model and an arbitration model, which are topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also introduces new performance metrics, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.MA).
